				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ch%C3%A2u-H%E1%BA%A3i-%C4%90%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng/Cam-th%E1%BA%A3o-t%E1%BB%AD/poem-cdLfHAqHlI69Vb0zo2kyDg">Cam thảo tử - 甘草子</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ch%C3%A2u-H%E1%BA%A3i-%C4%90%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng/author-ioE9gUDRRK0CF1f-0I-Dgw">Châu Hải Đường</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-T%E1%BA%A1o/%C4%90i%E1%BB%81n-gia-dao/poem-i5GNPkDIBNQnARwwV3xQAg">Điền gia dao - 田家謠</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-T%E1%BA%A1o/author-O82vYjarRAQfjsS_J_cIvQ">Trần Tạo</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-Duy-T%C3%B9ng/H%E1%BA%A1-t%C3%A2n-lang-Ti%C3%AAm-phu-t%E1%BB%AB/poem-jKy4QrLiBF2NMdCXGM2B9w">Hạ tân lang - Tiêm phu từ - 賀新郎－纖夫詞</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-Duy-T%C3%B9ng/author-cG-6f2ETrxSYJLcjUNmVzg">Trần Duy Tùng</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Ph%C3%BAc-%C6%AFng-B%C3%ACnh/Ho%E1%BA%A1-lang-trung-M%E1%BA%B7c-Si-ti%C3%AAn-sinh-d%E1%BA%A1-v%C5%A9-b%E1%BA%A5t-m%E1%BB%8B-%C4%91%E1%BB%99c-b%C3%A1o/poem-sDm1mVKun2Gcx4ztJ-BafA">Hoạ lang trung Mặc Si tiên sinh dạ vũ bất mị độc báo - 和郎中墨癡先生夜雨不寐讀報感作原韻</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Ph%C3%BAc-%C6%AFng-B%C3%ACnh/author-eQ6wft6d1E9_uEITUaRRlg">Nguyễn Phúc Ưng Bình</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/H%E1%BB%93-Thi%C3%AAn-Du/Li%E1%BB%87t-n%E1%BB%AF-L%C3%BD-Tam-h%C3%A0nh/poem-kAXSQG8h5bUMBdRjj9Vfhg">Liệt nữ Lý Tam hành - 烈女李三行</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/H%E1%BB%93-Thi%C3%AAn-Du/author-t5zNl0R6g-15oc9Dd33Eqg">Hồ Thiên Du</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-H%E1%BB%97/Quan-Ngu%E1%BB%B5-B%C3%A1c-H%C3%A0-t%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Bng-c%C3%B4ng-l%E1%BA%A1p/poem-AzatLkQjdpu8DLF6bwxeUg">Quan Nguỵ Bác Hà tướng công lạp - 觀魏博何相公獵</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-H%E1%BB%97/author-uSefdg6gWPnl7XHeM-UXCw">Trương Hỗ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Th%C3%B4ng/S%C6%A1n-trung-ng%E1%BB%99-v%C5%A9/poem-WrXoQa04ZdFt9WkOaQPqYQ">Sơn trung ngộ vũ - 山中遇雨</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Th%C3%B4ng/author-rfaS1tOCWjWB9PkLJ5MHxw">Nguyễn Thông</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Du/Tr%E1%BB%9F-binh-h%C3%A0nh/poem-wLBO_S7oDu5BwDnRbL0Axg">Trở binh hành - 阻兵行</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Du/author-ZRyB2U-4oqfhcjZ7xrf1_A">Nguyễn Du</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/V%C5%A9-Thu%E1%BB%B7-h%E1%BA%A1-thi%C3%AAn-h%C6%B0u-v%C5%A9/poem-cvMoxmTGDrxBU4uuCTFgeg">Vũ (Thuỷ hạ thiên hưu vũ) - 雨（始賀天休雨）</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Li%E1%BB%85u-V%C4%A9nh/V%C5%A9-l%C3%A2m-linh/poem-A7kddyY5Gu4Byp3YcjRB4A">Vũ lâm linh - 雨霖鈴</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Li%E1%BB%85u-V%C4%A9nh/author-ODOFEl8xHVsWXQUPgj9Ktg">Liễu Vĩnh</a>)<br></div>	</div>
